---
description: Tailwind CSS v4 usage rules for ID-Components
alwaysApply: true
---

Use Tailwind v4 utilities **only**. No `tailwind.config.js` or `tailwind.config.ts` — ever.

Theme tokens live in `packages/tokens/src/tokens.css` inside an `@theme {}` block. Reference them
through CSS variables in Tailwind utilities: `text-[var(--color-accent-500)]`, or via the
`@theme` aliases if defined (e.g., `bg-accent-500`).

Global CSS entry point pattern:
```css
@import 'tailwindcss';
@import '@id-components/tokens/tokens.css';
```

Never use `theme()` or `config()` functions — they belong to Tailwind v3.
